+#include "ansidecl.h"
+#include "libiberty.h"
+
+#if defined __STDC__ || defined ALMOST_STDC
+#include <stdarg.h>
+#else
+#include <varargs.h>
+#endif
+
+/* VARARGS */
+#ifdef ANSI_PROTOTYPES
+int
+asprintf (char **buf, const char *fmt, ...)
+#else
+int
+asprintf (buf, fmt, va_alist)
+     char **buf;
+     const char *fmt;
+     va_dcl
+#endif
+{
+  int status;
+  va_list ap;
+#ifdef ANSI_PROTOTYPES
+  va_start (ap, fmt);
+#else
+  va_start (ap);
+#endif
+  status = vasprintf (buf, fmt, ap);
+  va_end (ap);
+  return status;
+}
